MoveOn Statement: Donald Trump Is The Liar In Chief
By Brian Stewart. Tuesday, January 24 2017
Statement of Ilya Sheyman, Executive Director of MoveOn.org Political Action:

“From ‘Birtherism’ to ‘Illegal Voters,’ Donald Trump Is The Liar In Chief. In just five days, Trump has already started taking a wrecking ball to the office of the Presidency, our democracy, and our credibility at home and abroad. It is beyond shameful.”

